		glorious place?

A beat.

					MAXIMUS
		Yes, it's a glorious place.

					VALERIUS
		It must be.

He smiles.  And he is dead.

Maximus sits for a moment.  He gently closes Valerius'
eyes.  And Maximus finds that he is weeping.

He is not ashamed of the tears.

