				ROTH
		Honey, go down to the casino?

				TERRI
		If you feel better...

				ROTH
		I do.  Play the Bingo game.

They kiss, and she leaves.  Also Bussetta and Ola remain.

				ROTH
		My sixth sense tells me you have a
